</div>]]></content:encoded></item><item><title>App Store 去年成功防止大量詐騙　超過 80 萬惡意開發者帳戶被封鎖</title><link>https://unwire.hk/2022/06/04/apple-app-store-fraud-analysis/fun-tech/?utm_source=rss&amp;utm_medium=rss&amp;utm_campaign=apple-app-store-fraud-analysis</link><dc:creator><![CDATA[藍骨]]></dc:creator><pubDate>Sat, 04 Jun 2022 13:27:01 +0000</pubDate><category><![CDATA[科技趣聞]]></category><category><![CDATA[App Store]]></category><category><![CDATA[Apple]]></category><guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1103035</guid><description><![CDATA[<p>Apple 的 App Store 政策近年不斷受到挑戰，甚至有機會被法規強制要求容許用戶避開 App Store 自行安裝 App。Apple 最近就公佈新數據，顯示 App Store 成功防止了大量詐騙事件出現。</p></p>]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>Apple 的 App Store 政策近年不斷受到挑戰，甚至有機會被法規強制要求容許用戶避開 App Store 自行安裝 App。Apple 最近就公佈新數據，顯示 App Store 成功防止了大量詐騙事件出現。<br /><span id="more-1103035"></span></p><p>據 Apple 最近分享的數據顯示，App Store 在 2021 年制止了 160 萬次高風險和不可信的 App 對用家進行詐騙，其涉及的金額達到 16 億美元。而期間有超過 34,000 個 App 因為隱藏惡意功能被下架，另外也有近 16 萬個 App 因為抄襲其他 App 或者屬於垃圾 App 而被下架。</p><p><img loading="lazy" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/app-store-fraud-prevention.jpg" alt="" width="1306" height="1316" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1103036" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/app-store-fraud-prevention.jpg 1306w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/app-store-fraud-prevention-576x580.jpg 576w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/app-store-fraud-prevention-893x900.jpg 893w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/app-store-fraud-prevention-120x120.jpg 120w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/app-store-fraud-prevention-768x774.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 770px" /></p><p>Apple 一直強調，只容許開發者透過 App Store 為用家提供 App 安裝，是要保障用家免受惡意 App 所害，他們也將會繼續致力偵測詐騙活動，保持 App Store 安全，成為用家可以放心下載 App 的地方。</p><p>來源：<a href="https://www.macrumors.com/2022/06/01/apple-app-store-fraud-analysis/">MacRumors</a></p><p>unwire.hk Mewe 專頁：<a href="https://mewe.com/p/unwirehk" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"> https://mewe.com/p/unwirehk</a></p><h2> 最新影片</h2><iframe style="display: block; margin: 0px auto;" id="_ytid_84661" width="590" height="332" data-origwidth="590" data-origheight="332" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/?enablejsapi=1&amp;list=PLiEPZioiGtHw9_9gm4Ty0_pTEviOKNvfl&amp;autoplay=0&amp;cc_load_policy=0&amp;cc_lang_pref=&amp;iv_load_policy=1&amp;loop=0&amp;modestbranding=1&amp;rel=0&amp;fs=1&amp;playsinline=1&amp;autohide=1&amp;theme=light&amp;color=white&amp;controls=0&amp;" class="__youtube_prefs__  epyt-is-override  no-lazyload" title="YouTube player" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen="" data-no-lazy="1" data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll=""></iframe></p><div class="feedflare">
